// Default function

Default function parameter allow named parameter to be intialized with default 
value or undefined is passed



// rest parameter
it's represent infinite number of arrgument as an array.
ex:

const add =(...input) =>{
    // so here the given input are act as an array
    //so input parameter is like [1, 2, 3, 4, 5]
    console.log(input)
}

add(1, 2, 3, 4, 5)

